18.description:
Web and app system that allows access of third parties to private buildings using unique QR codes.
Instead of having to identify yourself at the front desk to a guard or a concierge, simply pass your phone with the QR code in our scanner at the entrance so you can access the building.
We verify your identity when you become a user, so you no longer have to do it at any front desk of any building with Entrify.
Once the code is scanned the system will show the concierge your name and picture, register your visit in the e-logbook and activates the door.
QR codes are unique for every specific access, even if it is the same person. Codes also expire if they are not used, hosts can set their duration.
